525
00:32:24,859 --> 00:32:28,240
At the sound of his true name, Boone started violently.

526
00:32:28,779 --> 00:32:30,679
For an instant, his eyes betrayed panic.

527
00:32:30,919 --> 00:32:33,019
Then he folded his arms with affected composure.

528
00:32:33,019 --> 00:32:37,180
