530
00:32:41,839 --> 00:32:46,180
With that, Holmes seized the man's chin in his firm grasp, heedless of his struggles,

531
00:32:46,400 --> 00:32:50,039
and began vigorously to scrub the distorted lip with the soapy cloth.

532
00:32:50,259 --> 00:32:53,420
The prisoner writhed and cursed, but Holmes' grip was unyielding.

533
00:32:53,779 --> 00:32:57,940
Presently, with a few rapid motions and a dash of the sharp-smelling spirits,

534
00:32:58,240 --> 00:33:01,000
the grime and pigment yielded and the hideous layer faded.

535
00:33:01,619 --> 00:33:06,440
Beneath the twisted mouth appeared the well-formed features of a man of education and refinement.

536
00:33:06,759 --> 00:33:09,319
The coarse hair was dragged away to reveal a smooth brow,

537
00:33:09,319 --> 00:33:14,839
and the rags seemed suddenly incongruous upon a body that bore itself with the instinctive carriage of a gentleman.

538
00:33:15,619 --> 00:33:19,240
Inspector Bradstreet sprang to his feet with an exclamation of amazement.

539
00:33:19,900 --> 00:33:22,079
