546
00:33:44,819 --> 00:33:47,179
Yes, I am Neville St. Saint

547
00:33:47,179 --> 00:33:51,099
Claire, though in this garb I am better known as Hugh Boone

548
00:33:51,099 --> 00:33:54,519
It is well, sir, that you acknowledge the truth

549
00:33:54,519 --> 00:33:57,119
Your wife's distress has been grievous

550
00:33:57,119 --> 00:34:00,659
and it is our duty to set her mind at rest.

551
00:34:01,279 --> 00:34:06,299
You owe us, therefore, a full and frank account of your strange deception.

552
00:34:07,659 --> 00:34:11,000
Sindham, Claire buried his face in his hands for a moment,

553
00:34:11,219 --> 00:34:14,199
then raised it with an expression of mingled shame and resignation.

554
00:34:15,019 --> 00:34:16,019
You shall know all.

