582
00:36:36,679 --> 00:36:37,839
Well, I'll be bound.

583
00:36:38,119 --> 00:36:40,059
In all my days, I've never seen the like.

584
00:36:40,059 --> 00:36:42,299
You think that a respectable gentleman

585
00:36:42,299 --> 00:36:43,759
should masquerade thus?

586
00:36:44,139 --> 00:36:45,879
