609
00:38:39,380 --> 00:38:41,640
while the city slumbered beneath its pall of mist,

610
00:38:42,079 --> 00:38:44,780
and thus ended the case of The Man with the Twisted Lip,

611
00:38:44,940 --> 00:38:47,440
a case which, for sheer singularity of circumstance,

612
00:38:47,920 --> 00:38:50,559
stands unmatched in my long association with Sherlock Holmes.

613
00:38:51,460 --> 00:38:55,280
