614
00:38:55,280 --> 00:38:58,200
though the air was still damp with the lingering breath of the Thames.

615
00:38:58,440 --> 00:39:01,260
Holmes, silent and contemplative, hung his coat upon the peg,

616
00:39:01,539 --> 00:39:04,220
lit the lamp, and flung himself into a familiar chair by the fire,

617
00:39:04,219 --> 00:39:07,559
followed, sinking wearily into my accustomed seat.

618
00:39:07,739 --> 00:39:09,139
The events of the last hours,

619
00:39:09,419 --> 00:39:10,939
the confrontation, the revelation,

620
00:39:11,139 --> 00:39:12,179
the strange confession,

621
00:39:12,599 --> 00:39:14,359
still weighed heavily upon my mind.

622
00:39:15,039 --> 00:39:17,519
