634
00:39:48,860 --> 00:39:54,140
In short, we must reason from facts, not from preconceptions.

635
00:39:55,760 --> 00:39:58,420
He leaned back, the smoke from his pipe,

636
00:39:58,680 --> 00:40:00,420
reading about his aesthetic features.

637
00:40:00,420 --> 00:40:05,500
You see, the case was not truly so impenetrable as it appeared.

638
00:40:05,760 --> 00:40:10,079
There was no murder, no abduction, no supernatural disappearance,

639
00:40:10,680 --> 00:40:14,740
merely a clever disguise, sustained by long practice.

640
00:40:15,400 --> 00:40:18,659
The clean hands betrayed him, the sovereigns gave him away,

641
00:40:18,900 --> 00:40:24,139
and the speed with which he transformed himself in that chamber was the final proof.

