660
00:42:09,619 --> 00:42:14,159
candle in hand, her face pale with long vigils, I took her trembling hand in mine.

661
00:42:15,019 --> 00:42:16,519
Madam, be comforted.

662
00:42:16,759 --> 00:42:19,279
Your husband lives and is safe, tinklers his self.

663
00:42:19,279 --> 00:42:21,400
