00:43:03,579 --> 00:43:05,360
Holmes said nothing as we re-entered the cab

685
00:43:05,360 --> 00:43:09,119
but his eyes softened and I thought I perceived in him a rare glow of satisfaction.

686
00:43:09,900 --> 00:43:13,199
Back at Baker Street, as dawn broke pale and worn across the housetops

687
00:43:13,199 --> 00:43:16,679
Holmes stretched himself upon the sofa and closed his eyes.

688
00:43:17,559 --> 00:43:19,019
Another case concluded.

689
00:43:19,340 --> 00:43:19,639
Watson

690
00:43:19,639 --> 00:43:26,440
Strange, grotesque, perhaps even sordid, but instructive.

691
00:43:27,219 --> 00:43:30,799
Let it stand in your notes as an example of the power of disguise

692
00:43:30,799 --> 00:43:35,299
