694
00:43:40,339 --> 00:43:42,199
It breeds deceits in every alley,

695
00:43:42,539 --> 00:43:47,539
and it is our task to tear away the mask, whether it hides crime or folly.

696
00:43:47,539 --> 00:43:50,659
